text:
37. Tyga then responded by distancing himself from the Kardashian family.

In a lengthy tweet he wrote: "I’ve never said anything about someone else’s child or family insinuating my involvement; and will never do so. Please, Stop spreading false stories and attacking people’s families. I have nothing to do with any of that. People should be able to live in peace." (Photo by Dave Kotinsky/Getty Images)
title: The Complete History Of Tyga & Kylie Jenner's Relationship
